# Piwigo ExtendedDescription

* Internal name: `ExtendedDescription` (directory name in `plugins/`)
* Plugin page: http://piwigo.org/ext/extension_view.php?eid=175
* Translation: http://piwigo.org/translate/project.php?project=extended_description

This plugin allows you to:
- have multilingual descriptions.
- have a small description for albums
- have full descriptions on an album page.
- have a description before and after thumbnails on an album page.
- hide an album.
- insert an image or an album link in a description.
- redirect an album

Extended Description may be used in page banner and in notification by mail.
